{"tid":648371,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"母親大人給了我一份「來自太空的禮物」","createTime":"2018-04-30T15:33:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T23:55:22.000Z","uid":1010,"like":2,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7614893bca46bc42cd01a3715370f19a5fdf691c","tid":648371,"uid":1010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T15:33:30.000Z","msg":"是咁的，岩岩老母話帶咗盒野俾我（唔好問邊到黎我都仲未搞清楚）<br />\n一見到盒野嘅標題心入面即刻打哂問號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但係又好雀躍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n竟然係祖國航天員科研訓練中心研發嘅產品！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/231744_83b5009e040969ee7b60362ad7426573.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F231744_83b5009e040969ee7b60362ad7426573.jpeg&h=4be6f382&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇唔夠5秒老母立刻開埋個盒，一睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/232159_ea571676ce9b75b0730a5d56350ae93e.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F232159_ea571676ce9b75b0730a5d56350ae93e.jpeg&h=71155e9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內部<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/232337_182845aceb39c9e413e28fd549058cf8.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F232337_182845aceb39c9e413e28fd549058cf8.jpeg&h=a290bfea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/232341_9679ccb5a92f650b83fcf29e0a6a6775.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F232341_9679ccb5a92f650b83fcf29e0a6a6775.jpeg&h=0c1af63e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當下我即刻懷疑我老母係咪航天局嘅員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後我就追問：咦，我飲完係咪可以變太空人先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知佢話：「咁又唔會...但係佢話太空人會飲架喎！我唔理啦，你同我早晚起身臨訓前都沖一條飲！有益架嘛！太空科技喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如是者，我就打算如果呢個post有300個正皮就實行老母嘅遵旨，每日早晚沖一條飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">希望我飲哂成盒之後可以成為首個香港藉嘅太空人！！！！！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbacd11feb546f90bd2ab0846c212dd3c82ce074","tid":648371,"uid":22566,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T15:35:17.000Z","msg":"因住飲到變太空生物添呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2216b9601f3d5da5b7ce786626bcc3b5bfc7ff2a","tid":648371,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:17:17.000Z","msg":"飲完肯靈雲上左太空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a042f4de2d0ecdc089c1bfd0f7928cbf0548f120","tid":648371,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:57:27.000Z","msg":"一陣飲完真係好似Red Bull咁送您一對翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b54f9242b6690f01d271efb264b0e7c3e5085b5","tid":648371,"uid":29717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T23:55:22.000Z","msg":"固體電解質<br />\n係咪姐係潮濕咗嘅寶礦力粉？"}]}